import React from 'react'; import '../Confirmation.css'; // Import the global styles function BookingConfirmed({ bookingDetails }) { const { name, email, phone, address, postalCode, bookingDate, timeFrom, timeTo, serviceName, servicePrice, totalArea, discount, amount, } = bookingDetails || {}; // Use an empty object fallback in case bookingDetails is undefined // Format the date const formattedDate = bookingDate ? new Date(bookingDate).toLocaleDateString('en-GB', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric', }) : 'No Date'; return (

Booking Confirmed

Thank you for booking with us, {name || 'N/A'}!

Name: {name || 'N/A'}
Email: {email || 'N/A'}
Phone: {phone || 'N/A'}
Address: {address || 'N/A'}
Postal Code: {postalCode || 'N/A'}
Date: {formattedDate}
Time Slot: {timeFrom || 'N/A'} - {timeTo || 'N/A'}
Service Name: {serviceName || 'N/A'}
Service Price (per m²): ${servicePrice || 'N/A'}
Total Area (sqm): {totalArea || 'N/A'} m²
Discount: {discount || 0}%
Total Amount: ${amount || 'N/A'}

We look forward to providing you with excellent service!

); } export default BookingConfirmed;
